        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrocracking reaction",
        "description": "在260°C、4 MPa H₂压力下，使用H-MCM-49沸石催化剂将棕榈酸升级转化为C₁₂-C₁₄烷烃。反应涉及脱氧、裂化和异构化。",
        "text_snippet": "The catalytic upgrading of palmitic acid over HM-49 and HMP-49 zeolites was conducted at 260°C for 4 h in the presence of 4 MPa H₂... HMP-49 obviously presented high palmitic acid conversion (>99%) and alkane selectivity (97.7%)... the selectivity of cracking (C₁₂−C₁₄) and the molar ratio isoalkanes/n-alkanes significantly improved",
