        "description": "在260°C、4 MPa H₂压力下，使用Ni/H-MCM-49双功能催化剂对棕榈酸进行升级。Ni颗粒增强了脱氧能力，同时沸石的酸性位点促进了裂化产物的异构化。",
        "text_snippet": "With impregnation of Ni particles, Ni/H-MCM-49 catalysts could enhance the activity and catalytic stability... complete deoxygenation of palmitic acid was achieved over Ni/H-MCM-49 with 100% selectivity of alkanes... The main products were C₁₂, C₁₃, C₁₄, C₁₅, and C₁₆ alkanes",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
